So when you hear that knocking
it's him hitting the side

00:09:52.800 --> 00:09:55.890
of the shadow puppet box and
that wakes the puppets up

00:09:55.890 --> 00:09:59.510
and invites the gods
to descend into them.

00:09:59.510 --> 00:10:12.880
[ Inaudible comment ]

