00:57:33.970 --> 00:57:39.540
&gt;&gt; I think the way I see it is
that in Bali the tradition is

00:57:39.540 --> 00:57:44.070
so old and everybody,
all the Balinese,

00:57:44.070 --> 00:57:49.280
the Hindu Balinese are
practicing it every hour

00:57:49.280 --> 00:57:51.330
of the day.

00:57:51.330 --> 00:57:55.780
So when they wake up, they
have all the tradition

00:57:55.780 --> 00:58:00.150
to give to whoever it is.

00:58:00.150 --> 00:58:07.160
They have what do you call them,
they have offering everywhere.

00:58:07.160 --> 00:58:10.910
So the tradition is very strong.

00:58:10.910 --> 00:58:16.220
And so that's why nobody - you
know, you have so many tourists

00:58:16.220 --> 00:58:26.620
and whatever, but it's very
strong so nobody can touch it.

00:58:26.620 --> 00:58:29.170
And when they dance
and [inaudible]

00:58:29.170 --> 00:58:35.150
and everything it's all to God.

00:58:35.150 --> 00:58:38.700
It's all for their God.

00:58:38.700 --> 00:58:40.790
You know, it's not
for the people.

00:58:40.790 --> 00:58:42.510
It's for God.

00:58:42.510 --> 00:58:48.030
And so, everything is for God,
and it's very [inaudible].

00:58:48.030 --> 00:58:54.330
And they practice every day,
every minute, every hour.

00:58:54.330 --> 00:59:00.110
It's the practice is
very - I mean it's -

00:59:00.110 --> 00:59:04.600
so nobody can touch it and
everybody leave them alone.

00:59:04.600 --> 00:59:08.500
Is that correct?

00:59:08.500 --> 00:59:15.200
Yes. But you go there, you see
all the offering everywhere,

00:59:15.200 --> 00:59:16.500
and [inaudible].

00:59:16.500 --> 00:59:22.460
You know like the one
[inaudible] the priest went

00:59:22.460 --> 00:59:26.860
up to see what's going on.

