00:59:34.820 --> 00:59:37.460
to go up because he wanted

00:59:37.460 --> 00:59:44.160
to do his own thing
according to his religion.

00:59:44.160 --> 00:59:46.750
So that's how I see it.

00:59:46.750 --> 00:59:49.520
