There's a lot of just
doing of the religions.

01:00:00.200 --> 01:00:02.630
The making of the
offerings and the praying,

01:00:02.630 --> 01:00:06.910
the temple ceremonies
it's every exhausting.

01:00:06.910 --> 01:00:12.900
And yet, I'm always meeting
people that - a cab driver

01:00:12.900 --> 01:00:15.900
on the way to the airport
after research this summer was

01:00:15.900 --> 01:00:17.870
from this traditional
village where I was sitting,

01:00:17.870 --> 01:00:22.250
but he was really getting
into this new Buddhist text

01:00:22.250 --> 01:00:25.020
that was coming out of
being published in China.

01:00:25.020 --> 01:00:28.540
It was kind of being introduced
into Indonesia, and he wanted

01:00:28.540 --> 01:00:31.200
to ask me about had I ever been

01:00:31.200 --> 01:00:34.200
to a charismatic Christian
service and what's that like?

01:00:34.200 --> 01:00:39.080
I mean, my experience as
an American is you're kind

01:00:39.080 --> 01:00:40.870
of totally assimilated
and there's not a lot

01:00:40.870 --> 01:00:44.430
of critical thought
or you reject it all

01:00:44.430 --> 01:00:46.940
and you're completely
idiosyncratic

01:00:46.940 --> 01:00:49.480
and you don't even
have a [inaudible].

01:00:49.480 --> 01:00:54.010
And to find people that are part
of very structured communities

01:00:54.010 --> 01:00:58.350
and yet have a real critical eye
and they're saying it's almost

01:00:58.350 --> 01:01:00.110
like they're in a buffet.

01:01:00.110 --> 01:01:04.270
I'll take a little bit of
this and a little bit of that.

01:01:04.270 --> 01:01:08.380
And maybe 10 years later, I'm
going to be a different person

01:01:08.380 --> 01:01:14.970
and I would have
learned other things.

01:01:14.970 --> 01:01:20.410
And I'll evolve as a spiritual
being even though I'm still

01:01:20.410 --> 01:01:22.800
doing these things within
a particular community.

01:01:22.800 --> 01:01:27.090
And for me as an American
that's so unique and different

01:01:27.090 --> 01:01:31.030
and I kind of have this
hang up and jealousy.

